data.description: Newly Renovated in 2021. This charming home features granite countertops, laminate hardwoods, generous trim through out, tiled master shower and large walk-in closets. This home is spacious with a den, family room with brick fireplace with gas hookups (or it could be used for an office/bedroom), open kitchen with stainless steel appliances, dining area, laundry closet 2 large bedrooms and 2 full baths. You must check out the large open master bathroom!!There is also a storage /sitting room off the rear of the home and a covered carport. Large open lot lined with trees and shrubs for privacy. Call today to schedule your private viewing. Sold AS IS!
